<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>药品质量检验报告</title>
<style>
body { font-family: SimSun, serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
h1 { text-align: center; }
h2 { border-bottom: 2px solid #003366; color: #003366; }
.pass { color: green; font-weight: bold; }
.fail { color: red; font-weight: bold; }
table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 15px 0; }
th, td { border: 1px solid #999; padding: 8px; }
th { background-color: #003366; color: white; }
.section { margin: 25px 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>药品质量监督抽检报告</h1>

<p><strong>检验机构</strong>：{{ by_type['regulatory_body'][0].name }}药品检验研究院</p>
<p><strong>报告编号</strong>：QC-{{ dates[15] }}</p>
<p><strong>抽检日期</strong>：{{ dates[16] }}</p>

<div class="section">
<h2>一、抽检概况</h2>
<p>本次抽检覆盖{{ by_type['region'][0].name }}、{{ by_type['region'][1].name }}、{{ by_type['region'][2].name }}的6家三甲医院药房及4家分销商仓库，共抽取样品32批次。</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h2>二、检验结果汇总</h2>

<table>
<tr>
  <th>药品名称</th>
  <th>生产企业</th>
  <th>批号</th>
  <th>抽检来源</th>
  <th>检验项目</th>
  <th>结果</th>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>{{ by_type['drug'][0].name }}</td>
  <td>{{ by_type['pharmaceutical_company'][0].name }}</td>
